2424420934616717875.Text: Tholer Saryoni told me that the Fourth Corner of the House of Troubles is Sheogorath. I must renew a pact with Sheogorath by finding a glove called the "Gambolpuddy" and donating it to Sheogorath's statue in Ald Daedroth. This shrine is on an island between Vvardenfell and Azura's Coast.

259563428213195461.Text: I made the Pilgrimage to Ald Daedroth and read a passage from the Four Corners of the House of Troubles. The pact with Sheogorath has been renewed.

12062236722614115036.Text: Temple: Sheogorath of the House of Troubles
